comments.body:
@zhenggu Thank you for contributing!

I have updated your PR summary to include the PR check list. Please update the checklist accordingly. I have also prepended your PR title with `WIP:` as you still have outstanding questions in your PR summary. When your PR is ready to merge, please remove the `WIP:`

Your PR makes changes to the code but does not include any tests. Please add tests to at least https://github.com/PowerShell/PowerShell/blob/master/test/powershell/Modules/Microsoft.PowerShell.Management/Split-Path.Tests.ps1. As this is a change in the `SessionStateNavigation.cs`, you may need to add tests to other cmdlets that this change affects.
